      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_27' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>1</sup> An additional &#x00A3;109 million from the Windfall Tax margin allocated in the 2002 Pre-Budget Report.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_28' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>2</sup> Excluding capital grants (in the Capital Line) and money
        transferred to EFS.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_29' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>3</sup> Subject to Parliamentary approval, the Department plans to
        use accumulated End Year Flexibility to supplement the funds
        available from the SR2002 settlement.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_30' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>4</sup> Includes miscellaneous support costs.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_31' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>5</sup> Excludes Standards Fund Gifted and Talented programmes.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_32' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>6</sup> Excluding PFI credits.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_33' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>7</sup> These figures are lower than those published in the LSC's Grant Letter issued on 5 December. The Grant Letter figures include an element of the funds transferred for teachers pensions contributions and CMF funding which is allocated outside the SR settlement.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_34' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>8</sup> This figure includes provision for VAT.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_35' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>9</sup> Includes Departmental spending on research and central spending on advertising and publicity.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_36' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>10</sup> Includes Departmental unallocated provision, Higher Education Baselines and funding to be allocated for Higher Education.
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_75ws' title='Col. 75WS &mdash; HC Deb 19 December 2002 vol 396 c75WS' name='column_75ws' href='#column_75ws' rel='bookmark'>75WS</a>
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_37' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>11</sup> This contributes towards the total Behaviour package of &#x00A3;13411491186 million announced on 12 December as the remainder is funded through the standards fund and other budgets.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0396P0_20021219_CWS_38' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <sup>12</sup> Not included in figures above. Excludes Education Maintenance Allowances which are funded through AME.
      </p>
